'''袁旃'''（{{bd|1941年||}}），生於重慶，是[[中華民國|台灣]]的視覺藝術家。她以創作[[水墨画|中國水墨畫]]而聞名。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Asia Society: New Chinese Art - Chronologies|url=http://sites.asiasociety.org/arts/insideout/chronologies.html|accessdate=2018-04-05|author=Inc.|first=Smith Renaud|work=sites.asiasociety.org|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127013323/http://sites.asiasociety.org/arts/insideout/chronologies.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她在台灣修讀中國畫，其後在[[比利时|比利時]]攻讀文物保育，並取得博士學位。完成學業回到台灣後，她在[[國立故宮博物院|台北國立故宫博物院]]的器物處工作了三十多年。她的作品借鑑古董原型和大師畫作，並以幾何圖案，鮮豔用色結合日常生活去詮釋視覺傳統。 <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2001/06/22/arts/art-in-review-china-without-borders.html|title=ART IN REVIEW; 'China Without Borders'|author=Cotter|first=Holland|date=2001-06-22|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2018-04-05|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2018-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627173653/https://www.nytimes.com/2001/06/22/arts/art-in-review-china-without-borders.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=International Symposium: Art and Translation in Taiwan, Hong Kong and Korea|url=http://www.taiwan-academy.eca.ed.ac.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Art-in-Translation-programme-14082017.pdf|date=2017|work=Taiwan Academy in Scotland|access-date=2021-03-13|archive-date=2018-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180505070458/http://www.taiwan-academy.eca.ed.ac.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Art-in-Translation-programme-14082017.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=The Weight of Lightness: Ink Art at M+ {{!}} Highlights|url=https://www.westkowloon.hk/en/inkart/highlights-2095/fair-and-clear-ii-yuan-jai-taiwanese-born-china-1941-lives-and-works-in-hsinchu-2006-22/page/10|accessdate=2018-04-05|author=Authority|first=West Kowloon Cultural District|work=www.westkowloon.hk|language=en|archive-date=2018-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180505070445/https://www.westkowloon.hk/en/inkart/highlights-2095/fair-and-clear-ii-yuan-jai-taiwanese-born-china-1941-lives-and-works-in-hsinchu-2006-22/page/10|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 學歷 ==
袁旃出生於[[四川省|四川]][[重庆市|重慶]]。她在[[國立臺灣師範大學|台灣省立師範學院]]藝術系（今[[國立臺灣師範大學|國立台灣師範大學美術學系]]）讀書時受到[[溥心畬|溥心畬]]和[[黄玉斌|黃君璧]]等國畫大師指導，其後移居到比利時，並在1966年於[[天主教魯汶大學|天主教魯汶大學（Université Catholique de Louvain）]]取得考古美術史碩士學位。1968年，她獲得比利時皇家文物維護學院（IRPA）的文化保育博士學位。[[装饰风艺术|裝飾藝術]]、[[新艺术运动|新藝術]]、[[立体主义|立體主義]]及[[超现实主义|超現實主義]]對她的作品影響甚深。 <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://ocula.com/artists/yuanjai/|title=Yuan Jai {{!}} Artworks, Exhibitions, Profile & Content|date=2018-04-05|accessdate=2018-04-05|language=en|archive-date=2018-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180505065956/https://ocula.com/artists/yuanjai/|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1998/09/18/arts/art-review-a-great-chinese-leap-into-a-new-sort-of-cultural-revolution.html|title=ART REVIEW; A Great Chinese Leap Into a New Sort of Cultural Revolution|author=Cotter|first=Holland|date=1998-09-18|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2018-04-05|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2018-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627151315/https://www.nytimes.com/1998/09/18/arts/art-review-a-great-chinese-leap-into-a-new-sort-of-cultural-revolution.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>http://www.vitamincreativespace.art/en/?artist=yuan-jai</ref>

== 作品 ==
袁旃在作品中使用顏色鮮豔的礦物[[色素|水粉]]（例如以[[孔雀石|孔雀石]]粉呈現綠色、以[[青金岩|青金石]]粉呈現藍色）來描繪藍綠色的景觀。 <ref>{{Cite book|title=Yuan Zhan = Yuan Jai : xian dai qing lü shan shui hua : gong yuan er qian nian liu yue nian san zhi qi yue er ri zhan lan.|last=Zhan.|first=Yuan|last2=袁旃.|date=2000|publisher=He Xiangning mei shu guan|isbn=9627376124|location=Shenzhen|oclc=56477597}}</ref>她的視覺語言融合了中國藝術傳統、歐洲油畫以及她的個人經歷。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Yuan Jai 1995-1997|url=https://aaa.org.hk/en/collection/search/library/yuan-jai-1995-1997-1995-1997|accessdate=2018-04-05|author=Archive|first=Asia Art|language=en|archive-date=2018-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180505081913/https://aaa.org.hk/en/collection/search/library/yuan-jai-1995-1997-1995-1997|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=Yuan Jai 1993|url=https://aaa.org.hk/en/collection/search/library/yuan-jai-1993-1993|accessdate=2018-04-05|author=Archive|first=Asia Art|language=en|archive-date=2018-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627204552/https://aaa.org.hk/en/collection/search/library/yuan-jai-1993-1993|dead-url=no}}</ref>她採用古典中國藝術元素，卻沒有遵循傳統的規則。她以跨地域方式詮釋中國藝術，因此挑戰了以歐美藝術史作為中心學說的地位。 <ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=International Symposium: Art and Translation in Taiwan, Hong Kong and Korea|url=http://www.taiwan-academy.eca.ed.ac.uk/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/Art-in-Translation-programme-14082017.pdf|date=2017|work=Taiwan Academy in Scotland}}</ref>袁旃直到四十歲才恢復繪畫創作，自1987年再次拿起畫筆以來，袁旃試圖以傳統為基礎，並結合她的生活經驗、技巧和知識去尋找創新的作畫方法。[http://www.vitamincreativespace.art/en/?artist=yuan-jai]

